                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7274" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1133</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9439 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化营销：三一重卡如何从红海中开创蓝海？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital marketing: How does Sany Heavy-Duty Truck Create a Blue Ocean from the Red Sea</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周文辉，冯露通，袁可纯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南行必达网联科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化营销；内容营销；差异化定位；三一重卡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital marketing; Content marketing; Differentiation positioning;  Sany Heavy-Duty Truck</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南行必达网联科技有限公司（以下使用品牌简称“三一重卡”）创
立于 2017 年 11 月，是三一集团实体经济与互联网深度融合、智能化与数字化转
型的先行者。从 2018 年 3 月 31 日首次网络直销开始，三一重卡不断刷新商用车
互联网销售纪录，创造了 36 秒售罄 1000 台的奇迹，开启了商用车互联网领域的
新篇章；2020 年，面对新冠肺炎疫情与发动机断供双重危机，三一重卡产销量突
破 2 万台，牵引车销量位列行业第六，成为重卡行业第二梯队“领头羊”；2021
年，三一重卡践行“双碳”战略，以 14.33%的市场份额夺得国内新能源重卡年度
销量冠军。三一重卡如何通过数字化营销从红海中开创蓝海？本文以问题为导向，
通过时间线与事件线详细描述了三一重卡数字化营销的背景、情境、过程、遇到
的决策问题及解决方法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Founded in November 2017, Sany HDT is the pioneer of the deep 
integration of the real economy and the Internet, as well as the intelligent and digital 
transformation of Sany Group. Since its first online direct sales on March 31, 2018, 
Sany HDT has continuously broken the Internet sales record of commercial vehicles 
and created the miracle of selling out 1,000 in 36 seconds, opened a new chapter in the 
field of commercial vehicle Internet. In 2020, in the face of the double crisis of COVID19 and engine supply failure, Sany&#39;s annual production and sales still exceeded 
20,000,and the sales volume of tractor ranked sixth in the industry, becoming the 
&quot;leader&quot; in the second tier of the HDT industry. In 2021, Sany carried out the &quot;double 
carbon&quot; strategy and won the annual sales champion of new energy heavy truck in 
China with 14.33% market share. How does Sany reverse attack from an industry 
latecomer to &quot;the millet of the truck industry&quot;? How does it create a blue sea from the 
red sea through digital marketing? This article is problem-oriented and describes the 
background, context, process, decision-making problems and solutions of the digital 
marketing of Sany HDT in detail through time line and event line.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化营销驱动因素；价值创新曲线；DTC创新模式；S2B2C商业模式；内容营销5A模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-04</td>
